data.description:
**Current VA note is assumable with a 3.25% interest rate!!**

Absolutely gorgeous 3 bedroom 3 bath condo over looking the golf course! Nestled in between the 18th tee box and the 10th green, this condo is equipped with hardwood floors, granite countertops through out, a large covered back porch as well as a good sized covered front porch and much more. The home has two primary bedrooms and the third bedroom has a bathroom attached as well. The primary bedroom upstairs is quite spacious and could also be used as a game room, and the primary bedroom downstairs has direct access to the back porch. With stunning views from any angle outside, don't be surprised to see wildlife as soon as you enter the gated White Bluff community. There's a local pub, restaurant, market, marina, and included in the HOA dues you get 36 rounds of golf and access to 4 pools (1 heated). Come see this one before it's gone!
